{
  "id": "RAW_3fc861",
  "title": "Kimi K2 模型更新，带来更强的代码能力、更快的 API",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Lac1gHCmuQ1mxTCWnSmuEA",
  "date": "2025-09-05 00:00:00",
  "author": "Kimi",
  "siteName": "月之暗面 Kimi",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905032740_a2cf90\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"100003738\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905032740_a2cf90\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">今天，我们发布 Kimi K2 模型的最新版本 0905，进一步提升其在真实编程任务中的表现：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Agentic Coding 能力提升：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在公开基准测试和真实的编程任务中均展现出更好的性能</span></span>\n    </section>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">前端编程体验升级：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">提升了前端代码的美观度和实用性</span></span>\n    </section>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">扩展上下文长度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：从 128K 升级到 256K，为复杂长线任务提供更好的支持</span></span>\n    </section>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">提供高速版 API：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">支持高达 60-100 Token/s 的输出速度</span></span>\n    </section>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n   <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在侧重考察真实软件工程任务的 SWE-bench Verified 等基准测试中，新版 Kimi K2 模型的表现如下：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"> \n     <br> \n    </span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905032740_672c02\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXgn2iaj6qPloIMS1aJqb9KibcrdBANjryPwg5fScukgaCRNtuXygPhN8lGoEe23mSDic5UicyEURWqFQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"325\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"100003734\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20250905032740_672c02\">\n   </section>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi 应用和网页版中的 K2 模型已全量升级到 0905 最新版，</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://kimi.moonshot.cn/download/app?from=wechat_official_account_menu\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下载 Kimi 应用</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或访问&nbsp;</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://www.kimi.com/\" textvalue=\"kimi.com\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">kimi.com</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;即可体验新版模型。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi 开放平台（</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://platform.moonshot.cn/\" textvalue=\"platform.moonshot.cn\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">platform.moonshot.cn</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">）已上架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;kimi-k2-0905-preview</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型 API：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上下文升级到&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">256K</span></span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Token Enforcer 保证&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">toolcall 100% 格式正确</span></span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">完全兼容 Anthropic API、</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">并支持 WebSearch Tool</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，提供更好的 K2 + Claude Code 使用体验</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">支持</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">全自动 Context Caching</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，有助于节省 Input Token</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">定价与之前的 0711 版相同</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">速度达&nbsp;</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">60-100&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Token/s</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;的高速版 API</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">（kimi-k2-turbo-preview）已同步升级新模型</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\">\n    <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n   </section>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如需自行部署模型，可在&nbsp;</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://huggingface.co/moonshotai\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Hugging Face</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://www.modelscope.cn/organization/moonshotai\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ModelScope</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;等平台下载。</span></span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\">\n    <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;HlJmdykTJoq1bgxM1DZcl2J8nRg&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;如需自行部署模型，可在 Hugging Face、ModelScope 等平台下载。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+8*0+4*0*2+c*0+1*0*3+a*0+7&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7325681545436282881&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;comment-id-7546289923230269444&quot;,&quot;true&quot;],&quot;2&quot;:[&quot;link&quot;,&quot;https%3A%2F%2Fhuggingface.co%2Fmoonshotai&quot;],&quot;3&quot;:[&quot;link&quot;,&quot;https%3A%2F%2Fwww.modelscope.cn%2Forganization%2Fmoonshotai&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:4}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;f55510ab-6864-4371-b786-d01f360084c1&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:25,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:42},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;XrssdE6lSokI95xzu3LclyurnIt&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n   </section>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0NDU1MDkyNg==&amp;mid=2247487284&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=961bb66c6decb3624fb2012d472394f7&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi K2 模型最初发布于 7 月 11 日</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，它是一款混合专家架构（MoE）的开源基础模型，总参数 10000 亿，激活参数 320 亿。目前，AI 编程工具 Cursor、Windsurf、Trae、Cline、RooCode、Kilo Code 等已内置或接入了 Kimi K2 模型。国内外云服务厂商均部署了 Kimi K2 模型，为开发者提供更多选择。</span></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n   <pre style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><code data-lark-language=\"Markdown\" data-wrap=\"true\"><p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 24px 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Kimi K2 资料夹</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">技术博客：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://moonshotai.github.io/Kimi-K2/\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">https://moonshotai.github.io/Kimi-K2/</span></a></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">技术报告：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.20534\" textvalue=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.20534\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.20534</span></a></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Github：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://github.com/moonshotai/kimi-K2\" textvalue=\"\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">https://github.com/moonshotai/kimi-K2</span></a></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">知乎讨论：</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/1927140506573435010\" textvalue=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/1927140506573435010\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/1927140506573435010</span></a></span></p></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Kimi K2 模型发布最新 0905 版本，全面提升代码能力、扩展上下文至 256K 并提供高速 API。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Kimi K2 模型发布最新 0905 版本，全面提升代码能力、扩展上下文至 256K 并提供高速 API。",
  "summary": "文章宣布了月之暗面 Kimi K2 模型的 0905 最新版本更新。此版本显著提升了模型在真实编程任务中的表现，包括增强 Agentic Coding 能力和优化前端编程体验。核心升级点还包括将上下文长度从 128K 扩展至 256K，以更好地支持复杂和长线任务。此外，Kimi 开放平台同步推出了支持 60-100 Token/s 输出速度的高速版 API，并具备 Anthropic API 兼容性、WebSearch Tool 支持及全自动 Context Caching 功能。文章还提及 Kimi K2 作为一款混合专家架构的开源基础模型，已被多种 AI 编程工具和云服务厂商集成。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Kimi K2 模型在 Agentic Coding 和前端编程能力上显著增强。",
      "explanation": "新版本在 SWE-bench 等基准测试中表现更优，提升了模型处理复杂编程任务的能力，并优化了前端代码生成质量和实用性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "上下文长度翻倍至 256K，大幅提升模型处理长文本能力。",
      "explanation": "扩展的上下文窗口使模型能更好地理解和处理复杂、长期的编程和文本任务，减少信息丢失和理解偏差，支持更宏大的项目。"
    },
    {
      "point": "开放平台提供高速版 API，并支持 Anthropic API 兼容与 WebSearch Tool。",
      "explanation": "高速 API 提升了开发效率，兼容性降低了迁移成本，WebSearch Tool 和 Context Caching 则进一步增强了模型的实用性和经济性，满足多样化开发需求。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Agentic Coding 能力提升：在公开基准测试和真实的编程任务中均展现出更好的性能",
    "扩展上下文长度：从 128K 升级到 256K，为复杂长线任务提供更好的支持",
    "提供高速版 API：支持高达 60-100 Token/s 的输出速度",
    "Kimi 开放平台（platform.moonshot.cn）已上架 kimi-k2-0905-preview 模型 API",
    "Kimi K2 模型最初发布于 7 月 11 日，它是一款混合专家架构（MoE）的开源基础模型，总参数 10000 亿，激活参数 320 亿。"
  ],
